{"about_the_game":"\u300aOpps! They love me way too much!\u300bis a live-action interactive film that simulates romantic relationships. <br>You will meet, get to know, and start sweet stories with four boys of different personalities and appearances in first person perspective. Among them, who will you ultimately choose as your Mr. Right?<br><br>Is it the sunny and adorable, passionately enthusiastic coffee shop clerk?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877720/extras/\u90b1\u77e5\u661fgif.gif?t=1723886941\" /><br><br>Is it the reserved and serious boss who seldom smiles?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877720/extras/\u5085\u6000\u5b89GIF.gif?t=1723886941\" /><br><br>Is it the cheerful and playful college classmate who knows you inside out?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877720/extras/\u53f6\u73c2gif.gif?t=1723886941\" /><br><br>Is it the gentle and family-oriented blind date partner who cooks for you?<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2877720/extras/\u6797\u6728gif.gif?t=1723886941\" /><br><br>Love E-boyfriend and enjoy the journey!<br><br><br><strong>Product Features</strong><br><br>1)Through the first-person immersive experience, you'll feel the excitement of romance, allowing you to experience the real-life emotional ups and downs and make crucial decisions.<br><br>2)Multiple branches and endings in the game open up infinite possibilities for exploration, adventure, and the pursuit of love.<br><br>3)With live-action performances, you'll be drawn into a vivid virtual world where each choice guides players towards different destinies, exploring various romantic paths, and sparking different flames of love with different boys.<br><br>4)Four boys with diverse personalities and appearances are available for ro